'''System Shock''' is an [[Achievement]] in the category ''[[Challenger: Series VI]]''. To complete this achievement, the player needs to defeat the [[Algorithm of Semi-Intransient Matrix of Overseer Network]] while it is paralyzed after it used its overclocking attack.
